      "id": "PopularPost144777",
      "post_content": "I could be wrong, but this seems to be the most reprinted Red Spell in the game.\n  \n   \nThis is FIRE, just as Lightning Bolt is LIGHTNING.\n  \n   \nIf I was given the keys to Richard Garfield's Vault (you know, the one where all these 15 Mythic Boxed Sets are coming from) and told to make some kind of 'Super Icons Deck' for each color, using cards that any new player could master in a day but the pro's would still play years later, I cannot possibly imagine not using 4x Lightning Bolt and 4x Fireball in the Red Deck.\n  \n   \nOut of all 17,000+ -something cards, Fireball and Lightning Bolt are two of a VERY select, magical few that can exist in a COMPLETE vacuum, outside of the context of THE ENTIRE GAME, and still make perfect sense and be awesome.\n  \n   \nLets Bungle in the Jungle\n  ",
      "posted_by": "DarthParallax",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost144777\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">I could be wrong, but this seems to be the most reprinted Red Spell in the game. \r<br/> <br/>This is FIRE, just as Lightning Bolt is LIGHTNING.\r<br/> <br/>If I was given the keys to Richard Garfield's Vault (you know, the one where all these 15 Mythic Boxed Sets are coming from) and told to make some kind of 'Super Icons Deck' for each color, using cards that any new player could master in a day but the pro's would still play years later, I cannot possibly imagine not using 4x Lightning Bolt and 4x Fireball in the Red Deck.\r<br/> <br/>Out of all 17,000+ -something cards, Fireball and Lightning Bolt are two of a VERY select, magical few that can exist in a COMPLETE vacuum, outside of the context of THE ENTIRE GAME, and still make perfect sense and be awesome. \r<br/> <br/>Lets Bungle in the Jungle\r<br/></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '144777'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy46041\">DarthParallax</span>\r\n                                (3/18/2011 11:58:00 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n              