    {
      "id": "PopularPost166502",
      "post_content": "Erik's Random card 6/3/2011  \nMagic 2010 was my first development lead. We have uncut sheets of Beta cards near where I work, and I would frequently walk by to compare the two sets to see if there was a good lesson to learn from Beta.  \n  \nSome of the common and uncommon cards in the design file were cut to simplify the set; there was a balance of simplicity and flavor, and those cards were not delivering on the fantasy flavor enough to justify their complexity.  \n  \nTo me, Fireball is the epitome of the flavor justifying the complication. While developers go over every card (except, perhaps, the basic lands), at no point was Fireball in jeopardy of leaving the set. It is awesome!  ",
      "posted_by": "ErikLauer",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost166502\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">Erik's Random card 6/3/2011<br/>Magic 2010 was my first development lead.  We have uncut sheets of Beta cards near where I work, and I would frequently walk by to compare the two sets to see if there was a good lesson to learn from Beta.<br/><br/>Some of the common and uncommon cards in the design file were cut to simplify the set; there was a balance of simplicity and flavor, and those cards were not delivering on the fantasy flavor enough to justify their complexity.<br/><br/>To me, Fireball is the epitome of the flavor justifying the complication.  While developers go over every card (except, perhaps, the basic lands), at no point was Fireball in jeopardy of leaving the set.  It is awesome!<br/></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '166502'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy62413\">ErikLauer</span>\r\n                                (6/5/2011 1:04:33 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00